title: Empire Earth 3 [for Mac]
description:
Move wrapper to desktop

Double click the wrapper --> install windows software --> navigate to the DVD or gamersgate file --> install the game --> set the start file as main .exe file --> run the game

Altough the gamersgate version works out of the box, For dvd version you might need a No-CD patch*. Get it from gamecopyworldand replace in the game folder the original file with the No-CD patch one.

Run the game!

Enjoy!

From: Paul the Tall

*When using a no-cd patch make sure you own the game and after patching keep it for yourself only.
